 663:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *
 664:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  The BLE Middleware is in the state #CY_BLE_STATE_INITIALIZING after the 
 665:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  Cy_BLE_Enable() is called and until the #CY_BLE_EVT_STACK_ON event is not 
 666:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  received. After successful initialization the state is changed to 
 667:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  #CY_BLE_STATE_ON.
 668:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *
 669:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  The BLE Middleware is in the state #CY_BLE_STATE_STOPPED 
 670:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  when the #CY_BLE_EVT_STACK_SHUTDOWN_COMPLETE event is received (after the 
 671:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  Cy_BLE_Disable() is called).
 672:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  
 673:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  For GAP Central role when the Cy_BLE_GAPC_ConnectDevice() is called, the state
 674:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  is changed to #CY_BLE_STATE_CONNECTING. After successful connection indicated
 675:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  by #CY_BLE_EVT_GAP_DEVICE_CONNECTED or #CY_BLE_EVT_GAP_ENHANCE_CONN_COMPLETE
 676:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  event or the timeout indicated by #CY_BLE_EVT_TIMEOUT event, the state is
 677:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *  changed to #CY_BLE_STATE_ON.
 678:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *
 679:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** * \return
 680:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** * \ref cy_en_ble_state_t : The current BLE Middleware state. The following are 
 681:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *                         possible states:
 682:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *
 683:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *   State                      | Description
 684:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble_gap.h **** *   -------------------------- | -----------
